      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be version-controlled, regression-tested, and hold a documented release qualification record.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Release notes, regression test suite results, and solver qualification documentation are archived. Achieved level 2 meets the MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
