      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must pass documented method-of-manufactured-solutions or benchmark tests relevant to rotating turbomachinery flows.",
      "rationale": "The solver has been verified against the ASME V&V 20 rotating-cavity benchmark and the FDA nozzle benchmark (CDER 2011). Observed order of accuracy is consistent with the nominal second-order scheme. Achieved level 2 meets requirement."
