      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry using a porcine blood analogue (haematocrit 33%) at the same five flow-speed operating points defined in the COU. Geometric and flow similarity is confirmed. Achieved level 2 meets requirement."
