    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cardiovascular-simulation-lab-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo sampling (1000 draws) has been completed and output variability in the relative hemolysis index is within acceptable bounds (95th-percentile RH = 0.87 < 1.0). The package is therefore accepted for regulatory submission. The team notes that formal sensitivity analysis to rank dominant input drivers is planned for the next revision cycle; this does not affect the current acceptance decision given the MRL 2 scope.",
